Package: SpotifyNetwork
Type: Package
Title: SpotifyNetwork 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ifeanyi Idiaye
Maintainer: Ifeanyi Idiaye <idiayeifeanyi@yahoo.com>
Description: The SpotifyNetwork package allows a user to query the Spotify API
             and return a network graph and data of artists that are related to
             a specific artist, using the artist's unique Spotify Id as the query
             argument.
